column2: SELECT   p.objID,   p.modelMag_u AS M_u,   p.modelMag_g AS M_g,   p.modelMag_r AS M_r,   p.modelMag_i AS M_i,   p.modelMag_z as M_z,   p.modelMagErr_u AS E_u,   p.modelMagErr_g AS E_g,   p.modelMagErr_r AS E_r,   p.modelMagErr_i AS E_i,   p.modelMagErr_z AS E_z,   p.z AS z_spec  INTO mydb.sdss1#_pmas_modelmag_#  FROM MyDB.sdss1#_pmas_phot_# AS p
